<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.1">
<l>vāṭama rutiṭai pōki mallaraik koṉṟokkalit tiṭṭu</l>
<l>āṭaṉṉaṉ māvuṭait tāya rāniraik kaṉṟiṭar tīrppāṉ</l>
<l>kūṭiya māmaḻai kātta kūttaṉe ṉavaru kiṉṟāṉ</l>
<l>cēṭuyar pūmpoḻil tillaic cittira kūṭattuḷ  ḷāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one who was able to come to be called the performer</l>
<l rend="indent">who guarded against the excessive, great torrent</l>
<l>To end the suffering that day for the herders and the cattle herd,</l>
<l rend="indent">having split the fine, prancing horse,</l>
<l>Killed the wrestlers, shouting [triumphantly],</l>
<l rend="indent">and gone between the marutu [trees] so that they withered,</l>
<l>He is the one present in Citrakūṭam in Tillai</l>
<l rend="indent">with gardens of graceful, tall flowers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
